Package: aactivator
Architecture: all
Depends: python2.7, python-setuptools
Description: automatically activate virtual environments
 aactivator automatically activates environments when entering and exiting
 directories.
 .
 By default, aactivator is not enabled. To opt-in to aactivator in your shell,
 add `eval "$(aactivator init)"` somewhere to your shell's rc files.
